name: Jakob Haq makes videos about mobile music creation on youtube : )
description: "My name is Jakob Haq and I am a mobile musician from Sweden with over +25 years of experience of computerized music making. For the past four years I've mainly make music using portable hardware, with an iPad as a central platform. On this channel you'll find video tutorials, reviews and let's play's featuring  portable music hardware  (Pocket operators, volcas, etc) and also a huge amount of videos featuring imusic apps and iDevices (iPad and iPhone). iOS is pretty much a central hub in my production and have been or the past 6 yers. All of my content including music, videos and animations are filmed, made, edited and finalised using iOS entirely." https://www.youtube.com/c/JakobHaq
